{"tid":706639,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三父子同人嘈 中伏被電筒扑傷頭","createTime":"2018-06-18T05:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T05:16:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a804a9eb90ffbfb15b2fa85253c7191547e8013","tid":706639,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20424147\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20424147&d=Et%2ByH5%2BYN80hIswW0Xm636NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=946a93bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20424147&h=ff63372f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20424147</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月18日 <br />\n<br />\n三父子同人嘈<br />\n中伏被電筒扑傷頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】葵涌廣場對開發生傷人案，昨晨2時許，一名姓張45歲男子，偕同兩名18及16歲兒子行經，遭到三名兇徒襲擊，有人持電筒作武器，三父子同告頭部受傷，兇徒傷人逃去。警方接報到場，將傷者送院。據稱三父子早前因瑣事與人爭吵。警方調查案件追緝兇徒下落。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n縱火狂燒18架電單車　對面係將軍澳警署<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n揸500萬「狂牛」飆車　警截車拉人"}]}